      • newIntent

        @NonNull
public static android.content.Intent newIntent(@NonNull
                                                        android.content.Context context,
                                                        boolean requirePostalField,
                                                        boolean updatesCustomer)
        Create an Intent to start a AddSourceActivity.
        Parameters:
        context - the Context used to launch the activity
        requirePostalField - true to require a postal code field
        updatesCustomer - true if the activity should update using an already-initialized CustomerSession, or false if it should just return a source.
        Returns:
        an Intent that can be used to start this activity
